{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T05:10:56.062175", "event": "AGENT_OBSERVATION", "data": {"step": 1, "tool": "search_lab_docs", "args": "led", "observation": "K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho 'led':\n- (Lab 1 | M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch) Th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi LED \u0111\u01a1n v\u00e0 LED 7 thanh.\n- (Lab 1 | M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch) X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi LED 7 thanh v\u00e0 remote control.\n- (Lab 1 | 3.0 Project m\u1eabu) Import Lab1_20242.zip v\u00e0o STM32CubeIDE. D\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y: LED3/LED4 \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i khi b\u1ea5m \u0111\u00fap n\u00fat B1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang. PA0 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh External interrupt + Rising edge; CPU 180 MHz, timer 90 MHz; Timer 6 sinh ng\u1eaft 10000 Hz; x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ea5m \u0111\u00fap trong stm32f4xx_it.c.\n- (Lab 1 | 3.1 Gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i LED \u0111\u01a1n) Gh\u00e9p 8 LED \u0111\u01a1n v\u1edbi PD8\u2013PD15 (qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf 330\u03a9). C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh PD8\u2013PD15 l\u00e0 GPIO_Output. Khai b\u00e1o bi\u1ebfn LED_Value, th\u00eam h\u00e0m DisplayLEDs(int mode) v\u00e0 g\u1ecdi trong main loop \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng LED ch\u1ea1y.\n- (Lab 1 | 3.2 Gh\u00e9p n\u1ed1i LED 7 thanh) Gh\u00e9p 2 module LED 7 thanh: c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n thanh n\u1ed1i PE8\u2013PE15, ch\u00e2n ch\u1ecdn module n\u1ed1i PG2 v\u00e0 PG3 (qua transistor NPN). Th\u00eam 7seg.h/7seg.c, d\u00f9ng HAL_TIM_Base_Start_IT(&htim6) + Set7SegDisplayValue(25) + Run7SegDisplay() \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb s\u1ed1 25."}}
